<HEAD>Body Found Near Berlin Wall</HEAD>
<DATELINE>BERLIN (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   West Berlin authorities today removed the body of
an apparent suicide victim found hanging from a tree near the
Berlin Wall, a police spokesman said.
   West Berlin officials negotiated with counterparts in communist
East Berlin for two hours before they were allowed to take down the
